des:
Listen to an interactive spooky story with sound effects and prompts. When you open the skill, Alexa asks for character names and other information to fill in the blanks. Get ready for laughs and giggles as your audience fills in the blanks and listens to their customized story.
Are you a fan of horror stories, of abductions and mysterious disappearances. Then listen to this scary tale of the hospice world, and the innocent trapped there, for no fault of theirs. Maybe you may vanish too to be domiciled somewhere, you may even forget your past. Listen on to a horror story of such forgotten people.
